<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-70-0311 </DOCNO><TEXT>This exhibit is an interactive video on management of a patient with alung nodule. It emphasizes radiological and clinical features of thesolitary pulmonary nodule. The program allows history taking, obtainingphysical findings, tests, management, and an extensive review of factualmaterial. A computer-based lesson interacts through natural languageprocessing with immediate feedback. References, tables, and charts toelucidate factual material are provided. A laser disk provides videosegments of patient interviews, radiographs, pathologic specimens, andactual procedures. The system monitors omissions, commissions, and thesequence of investigation and management decisions. Performance can beevaluated with the program.</TEXT></DOC>